Package: ompReadGA
Title: Tools for Fast BAM File Processing and Conversion to GAlignments using Multiple Threads
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Byungjun", "Kim", , "byungjunkim07@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0009-8477-7282"))
Description: Provides tools to process BAM files efficiently using C++ framework
    via the 'ompBAM' library. Includes functions to extract alignment data and 
    convert it into GAlignments objects for downstream genomic analysis.
